{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Tax cyclists for road use ",
        "additional_details": "The Government needs money and I believe that cyclists should have to pay a personal tax to ride their bikes on the roads. They use our roads, they have cycle lanes that are all painted up for them in a lot of places. It doesn\u2019t have to be expensive, e.g. \u00a330 per year or more; but, if everyone who rides a bike paid it, then I believe it surely would put more money in the Government\u2019s bank.",
        "background": "We want the Government to tax cyclists, a personal tax for every adult who rides a bicycle on roads.",
